general-type=3D"meta_field" data-hs-cos-type=3D"rich_text"><h4 style=3D"fon=
t-size: 24px; text-align: center;">Discover how many items you can take on =
your next vacation using a handy vacation packing calculator.</h4>
<!--more-->
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style=3D"color: #000000;">Packing can turn an <a href=3D"https://w=
ww.wayfairertravel.com/inspiration" rel=3D"noopener"><span style=3D"font-we=
ight: bold;">exciting vacation</span></a> into a game of guesswork=E2=80=94=
what to bring, what to skip, and how to keep your bag under the limit. A sm=
art plan makes all the difference. Start with a simple checklist, edit for =
your itinerary and weather, and lay everything out before it goes in the su=
itcase. Aim for mix-and-match outfits, pack shoes that pull double duty, an=
d decant liquids to travel sizes. Weigh your bag at home so airport scales =
don=E2=80=99t surprise you.<br><br></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: #000000;">Use our helpful Wayfairer packing list f=
or any trip. We developed this based on airline rules that might affect bag=
gage size or weight. We=E2=80=99ll help you decide what=E2=80=99s essential=
 for your destination and season, and what can stay home. If you like tools=
, we also include a quick packing calculator and a printable checklist to k=
eep you on track. You=E2=80=99ll find these helpful if you=E2=80=99re close=
 to the weight limit or traveling with kids.<br><br></span></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: #000000;">Take the stress out of packing, and you=
=E2=80=99ll start your vacation lighter, organized, and ready to go.<br></s=
pan></p>
<div data-hs-responsive-table=3D"true" style=3D"overflow-x: auto; max-width=
